      pains:["Cloud-first SAP strategy (BTP, RISE)","S/4HANA migration","Resource gaps for specific modules","Staff aug for program surge"],
      ourStory:"Malla is at HPE on IS-U + S/4HANA. Quick placement, no ramp time.",
